column4: Hi all I have a quick question I am following a tutorial for my server install. One of the packages that is meant to be installed is libkadm55 however because this is a dated tutorial ubuntu says that the package no longer exists is anyone able to tell me how I can find an alternative if there is one?
use an up to date tutorial?  What are you trying to accomplish?
what version of ubuntu are you using exactly?   That package exists in the latest ubuntu
